			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="This is a frog in the hag's swamp. When the hag is not defeated she is fighting the hag's control - hissing and ribbiting in pain as she struggles not to hurt anyone.&#xD;&#xA;When the hag is defeated, she is cheerfully ribbiting as she hops about the swamp.&#xD;&#xA;In the top two nodes, she is showing the player a stash of loot as a reward for freeing her from the hag. Only available with SwA." />
